data.description: Are you looking for a BEAUTIFUL home in a QUIET Subdivision on almost a HALF ACRE LOT? Here it is!! Located in the beautiful Summerlin Subdivision, this 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bathroom home is sure to impress! Walk into the oversized foyer off of the covered porch to a welcoming farmhouse vibe. The family room features a stunning fireplace with shiplap & tile! And large windows for lots of natural light. Open concept living on the main level. Gorgeous granite countertops and subway tile in the kitchen. The primary bedroom and bathroom are located on the 2nd floor along with 3 more spacious bedrooms. The home is on a fenced in corner lot. Great location to commute to Ft Liberty, Sanford, or Raleigh. Just 12 minutes from restaurants and shopping on Buffalo Lake Rd. Less than 100 feet from the Aloha zoo! This incredible property is a MUST SEE!!
